      "english": "eye",
      "word": "l'œil (masc.)",
      "grammarNote": "l'œil (singular) and les yeux (plural) are completely different words — one of the most irregular plurals in French. 'Il a les yeux bleus' = He has blue eyes.",
      "englishPhrase": "He has blue eyes.",
      "phrase": "Il a les yeux bleus."
    },
